overview: When it comes to an orgy of lust-crazed encounters, "The Princess of the Night" knows all the moves! In the ring or in the sack, Tori Welles and her beautiful wresting girl co-stars body slam their way into many an erotic adventure. You'll soon see that if you can get past round one with Tori Welles, you can do anything!
tagline: A Wrestling Sextravaganza - With No Holds Barred!
title: Head Lock
